{"synckey":1745658905,"updated":[{"bookId":"3300140481","bookmarkId":"3300140481_5_1541-1586","createTime":1745658905,"chapterUid":5,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"把自己视作故事中的人物，将自己的事当作别人的事，这样你就可以客观地处理所遇到的各类问题了。","range":"1541-1586"},{"bookId":"3300140481","bookmarkId":"3300140481_5_1264-1325","createTime":1745658895,"chapterUid":5,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"从“故事思维”的立场来看，没有挑战和失败才是风险。这是因为，就故事的可读性而言，风平浪静的人生简直无聊透顶。","range":"1264-1325"},{"bookId":"3300140481","bookmarkId":"3300140481_5_949-984","createTime":1745624222,"chapterUid":5,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"只有站在客观角度来审视自身，才对解决本质问题更有帮助”。","range":"949-984"},{"bookId":"3300140481","bookmarkId":"3300140481_5_777-869","createTime":1745624215,"chapterUid":5,"colorStyle":3,"type":1,"markText":"“故事思维”是指，如果想过上梦寐以求的生活，那么不妨把人生当成正在写的故事，而自己作为这个故事的主人公，就像“推动故事情节发展”一样，正推动着自己的人生进程。这就是“故事思维”的奥义。","range":"777-869"}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"序幕 什么是“故事思维”","chapterUid":5,"chapterIdx":5}],"book":{"bookId":"3300140481","version":1949375646,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/91/cpplatform_q4jywwsgg5ceqjfcctq5na/s_cpplatform_q4jywwsgg5ceqjfcctq5na1744188343.jpg","title":"用故事思维设计你的人生","author":"[日]古川健介","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KJL=qJK7K,$*e.OEGwrWrV","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#002131"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#00233c"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#002547"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#003645"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#003850"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#003a5d"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#154e5e"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#005069"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#005275"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#00578c"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#006981"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#006e99"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#356776"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#0089b2"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#51808e"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#0086a6"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#6b9ba8"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#4c9eb4"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#00a1c0"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#00a7d8"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#3ebcd9"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#00bfe7"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#00c3f5"},{"key":"8